github_body:
Map changes:
    * #423 Route synchronization is no longer attempts to connect for people who are not logged in.
    * #431 Virtual tour is now once again accepting visitors!
    * #423 Added a new option to your profile to allow you to show you as Anonymous when connecting to routes not part of any of your teams. Enabled by default.

changes.change: Route synchronization is no longer attempts to connect for people who are not logged in.
Virtual tour is now once again accepting visitors!
